	========== NCR Salvaged Power Armor ==============
	===============================================-->	

  <ThingDef ParentName="JDSNCRApparelBase">
		<defName>JDS_NCR_SalvagedPowerArmor</defName>
		<label>NCR Salvaged Power Armor</label>
		<description>"NCR salvaged power armor is T-45d power armor recovered by the NCR during the NCR-Brotherhood War. NCR technicians stripped out the servomotors and replaced the rad scrubbers with a custom air conditioning module, allowing it to be used by soldiers without the need of Power Armor Training. The process, however, dramatically reduces its effectiveness, as "It feels like you're carrying a brahmin on your back"."</description>  
